A few weeks ago, we told you we were heading to Pittsburgh, PA on
December 12, 2000 with three daily, round-trip flights from New York
City; three daily, round-trip flights from Chicago; and two daily,
round-trip flights from Atlanta.  Now, we are introducing our newest
city to you by putting Pittsburgh on sale for travel from December 12,
2000 through March 14, 2001!!!!  This sale requires a minimum 7-day
advance purchase and fares start as low as $39 one way.  You must
purchase http://www.airtran.com/reservations/cgi-bin/flight_search.cgi
tickets by December 19, 2000.

Receive a BONUS 5% discount if you make your sale fare booking online
at www.airtran.com  !!!!!!!

Remember:  Travel may originate in either city and all fares are
one-way and don't require a roundtrip purchase.

